00:46:00.000 --> 00:46:01.270
That's not the way to
think about it.

00:46:01.270 --> 00:46:03.340
Say, if you make
this assumption

00:46:03.340 --> 00:46:05.900
you get these curves.

00:46:05.900 --> 00:46:07.180
And then figure out
what it means.

00:46:07.180 --> 00:46:10.535
You can't make everything
anthropomorphic.

00:46:10.535 --> 00:46:14.630
If this were the case, and
furthermore if the energy of

00:46:14.630 --> 00:46:18.700
one of these quanta was related
to its frequency--

00:46:18.700 --> 00:46:21.790
and wavelength and frequency
are inversely related--

00:46:21.790 --> 00:46:25.020
then the proportionality
constant is h, which we now

00:46:25.020 --> 00:46:28.170
have designated the Planck
constant in honor of Planck,

00:46:28.170 --> 00:46:30.200
then you get this.

00:46:30.200 --> 00:46:32.270
People grew to accept it.

00:46:32.270 --> 00:46:34.430
1900, he gets a Nobel
Prize for it.

